Privacy Policy for GPTs Works

Effective Date: 2023/11/11

This Privacy Policy describes how we collects, uses, and discloses information through our Google Chrome Extension, GPTs Works.

1. Information Collection

When you use our Extension, we may collect the following types of information:

  • Personal Information: This may include your name, email address, and any other information you provide when using our Extension.
  • Browsing Data: We may collect information related to the websites you visit and how you interact with content while using our Extension.
  • Usage Data: This includes information about how you use our Extension, such as the features you use and the time spent on the Extension.

2. Use of Information

The information we collect is used for the following purposes:

  • To provide, maintain, and improve the Extension.
  • To respond to your inquiries and provide customer support.
  • To conduct research and analysis to enhance the functionality of our Extension.
  • For any other purpose with your consent.

3. Information Sharing

We may share your information with third parties in the following situations:

  • With Service Providers: We may share your information with third-party service providers who perform services on our behalf.
  • For Legal Reasons: We may disclose your information if required by law or if we believe it’s necessary to prevent fraud or other illegal activities.
  • In Business Transfers: If we are involved in a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets, your information may be transferred as part of that transaction.

4. Data Security

We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure.

5. Children’s Privacy

Our Extension is not intended for children under the age of 13, and we do not knowingly collect information from children under 13.

6. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

7. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at yixotieq@gmail.com.
